<!doctype html>
<html lang="<%= lang || 'uk' %>">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg?v=<%= encodeURIComponent(String(appVersion || '0.0.0')) %>" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <%- include('partials/theme-bootstrap-head', { defaultTheme: 'dark' }) %>
    <title>Studerria Vision</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/vision-bg.css" />
    <%- include('partials/studerria-system-head') %>
  </head>
  <body class="studerria-theme theme-dark page-vision" data-theme="dark">
    <%- include('partials/theme-bootstrap-body') %>
    <%- include('partials/vision-bg') %>

    <div class="vision-shell">
      <header class="vision-header st-nav" data-ascii-safe>
        <a href="/" class="vision-logo" aria-label="Studerria home">
          <img src="/favicon-dark.png" alt="" class="vision-logo-mark vision-logo-mark--dark" />
          <img src="/favicon-light.png" alt="" class="vision-logo-mark vision-logo-mark--light" />
          <span>STUDERRIA</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="vision-nav" aria-label="Design system sections">
          <a href="#schedule">Розклад</a>
          <a href="#admin">Адмінка</a>
          <a href="#login">Логін</a>
          <a href="#profile">Профіль</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="vision-header-actions">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="theme-toggle"
            id="visionThemeToggle"
            data-light-label="Світла"
            data-dark-label="Темна"
            aria-label="Toggle theme"
          >
            Світла
          </button>
          <a class="signup-btn" href="/login">Open app</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="vision-main">
        <section class="vision-hero" id="visionHero" aria-label="Studerria hero">
          <div class="vision-hero-copy ascii-overlay-safe" data-ascii-safe>
            <div class="vision-hero-brand">
              <div class="vision-hero-brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
                <img src="/favicon-dark.png" alt="" class="vision-hero-logo vision-hero-logo--dark" />
                <img src="/favicon-light.png" alt="" class="vision-hero-logo vision-hero-logo--light" />
              </div>
              <span class="vision-hero-wordmark">STUDERRIA</span>
            </div>
            <p class="st-kicker">Studerria product surface</p>
            <h1>Спокійний інтерфейс для навчання щодня.</h1>
            <p class="vision-hero-body">
              Один візуальний шар для логіну, розкладу, адмінки й профілю: чиста ієрархія, м’який glass-material і
              стриманий cursor-driven ASCII фон без зайвого шуму.
            </p>
            <div class="vision-hero-actions" data-ascii-safe>
              <a class="signup-btn vision-hero-cta" href="/login">Open app</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="vision-hero-preview-wrap ascii-overlay-safe" data-ascii-safe>
            <article class="vision-hero-preview st-surface-elevated" aria-label="Studerria dashboard preview">
              <div class="vision-preview-topbar">
                <div class="vision-preview-brand">
                  <img src="/favicon-dark.png" alt="" class="vision-preview-logo vision-preview-logo--dark" />
                  <img src="/favicon-light.png" alt="" class="vision-preview-logo vision-preview-logo--light" />
                  <span>Studerria</span>
                </div>
                <div class="vision-preview-search">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">⌘K</span>
                  <span>Search anything…</span>
                </div>
                <span class="vision-preview-pill">Vision</span>
              </div>

              <div class="vision-preview-grid">
                <aside class="vision-preview-sidebar">
                  <div class="vision-preview-sidebar-item is-active">Vision</div>
                  <div class="vision-preview-sidebar-item">Schedule</div>
                  <div class="vision-preview-sidebar-item">Tasks</div>
                  <div class="vision-preview-sidebar-item">Messages</div>
                  <div class="vision-preview-sidebar-item">Profile</div>
                </aside>

                <div class="vision-preview-content">
                  <div class="vision-preview-intro">
                    <div>
                      <p class="st-kicker">Morning overview</p>
                      <h2>Good morning, Andrii</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>Один спокійний dashboard з чистою ієрархією, м’яким glow і системними surfaces.</p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="vision-preview-metrics">
                    <article><span>Classes today</span><strong>4</strong><em>+1 from yesterday</em></article>
                    <article><span>Study time</span><strong>5h 30m</strong><em>+1h 20m</em></article>
                    <article><span>AI insights</span><strong>12</strong><em>New recommendations</em></article>
                    <article><span>Tasks done</span><strong>8</strong><em>Steady cadence</em></article>
                  </div>

                  <div class="vision-preview-panels">
                    <article class="vision-preview-schedule">
                      <header>
                        <h3>Today’s schedule</h3>
                        <span class="st-pill">View full schedule</span>
                      </header>
                      <div class="vision-preview-rows">
                        <div><span>09:00</span><strong>Mathematics</strong><em>Lecture · Room 201</em></div>
                        <div><span>11:00</span><strong>Physics</strong><em>Lecture · Room 305</em></div>
                        <div><span>13:00</span><strong>Computer Science</strong><em>Lab · Room 118</em></div>
                      </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="vision-preview-assistant">
                      <span class="vision-preview-spark">✦</span>
                      <h3>AI Study Assistant</h3>
                      <p>You’ve been focusing well. Review Calculus basics before tomorrow’s class.</p>
                      <a href="/login" class="signup-btn">Ask AI anything</a>
                    </article>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="vision-samples" aria-label="Studerria surface samples">
          <div class="vision-section-head ascii-overlay-safe" data-ascii-safe>
            <div>
              <p class="st-kicker">Surface samples</p>
              <h2>Reusable product primitives below the hero.</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="vision-section-copy">
              Тут уже не концепт-hero, а приклади реальних поверхонь: читабельні, щільні там де треба і спокійні в обох темах.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="vision-reference-grid">
            <article class="vision-product-panel vision-product-panel--schedule" id="schedule" aria-label="Schedule reference">
              <header class="vision-showcase-head">
                <div>
                  <p class="st-kicker">Навчання</p>
                  <h2 class="st-title">Тиждень 14</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="vision-control-cluster">
                  <span class="st-badge">Сьогодні</span>
                  <span class="vision-icon-pill" aria-hidden="true">‹</span>
                  <span class="vision-icon-pill" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
                </div>
              </header>

              <div class="vision-days" aria-label="Week cards">
                <div class="vision-day is-active"><strong>Пн</strong><span>14 квіт · 4 пари</span></div>
                <div class="vision-day"><strong>Вт</strong><span>15 квіт · 4 пари</span></div>
                <div class="vision-day"><strong>Ср</strong><span>16 квіт · 3 пари</span></div>
                <div class="vision-day"><strong>Чт</strong><span>17 квіт · 5 пар</span></div>
                <div class="vision-day"><strong>Пт</strong><span>18 квіт · 4 пари</span></div>
                <div class="vision-day"><strong>Сб</strong><span>19 квіт · —</span></div>
                <div class="vision-day"><strong>Нд</strong><span>20 квіт · —</span></div>
              </div>

              <div class="vision-lessons">
                <article class="vision-lesson">
                  <div class="vision-lesson-number">1</div>
                  <div>
                    <h3>Правознавство</h3>
                    <p>10:00 - 11:20 · група 1 · ауд. 201</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="st-badge">Лекція</span>
                </article>
                <article class="vision-lesson">
                  <div class="vision-lesson-number">2</div>
                  <div>
                    <h3>Політологія</h3>
                    <p>11:40 - 13:00 · група 2 · ауд. 305</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="st-badge">Семінар</span>
                </article>
                <article class="vision-lesson">
                  <div class="vision-lesson-number">3</div>
                  <div>
                    <h3>Іноземна мова</h3>
                    <p>15:10 - 16:30 · група 3 · ауд. 409</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="st-badge">Практика</span>
                </article>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="vision-product-panel vision-product-panel--admin" id="admin" aria-label="Admin reference">
              <header class="vision-showcase-head">
                <div>
                  <p class="st-kicker">Control center</p>
                  <h2 class="st-title">Адмін-панель</h2>
                </div>
                <span class="vision-status-pill">Session OK</span>
              </header>

              <div class="vision-admin-layout">
                <aside class="vision-admin-sidebar" aria-label="Admin sidebar preview">
                  <span class="vision-select">ППБД 25 Київ</span>
                  <a class="is-active" href="#admin">Overview</a>
                  <a href="#admin">Academic Setup</a>
                  <a href="#admin">Import/Export</a>
                  <a href="#admin">Homework</a>
                  <a href="#admin">Messages</a>
                </aside>
                <div class="vision-admin-content">
                  <div class="vision-metrics">
                    <div><span>Users</span><strong>30</strong></div>
                    <div><span>Subjects</span><strong>8</strong></div>
                    <div><span>Homework</span><strong>0</strong></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vision-tools">
                    <span>Генератор розкладу</span>
                    <span>Генератор сесій</span>
                    <span>Import/Export</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vision-nearest">
                    <h3>Найближчі пари</h3>
                    <p>Сьогодні, 10:00 - 11:20 · Правознавство · ауд. 201</p>
                    <p>Сьогодні, 11:40 - 13:00 · Політологія · ауд. 305</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="vision-product-panel vision-product-panel--login" id="login" aria-label="Login reference">
              <div class="vision-auth-card">
                <img src="/favicon-dark.png" alt="" class="vision-auth-logo vision-auth-logo--dark" />
                <img src="/favicon-light.png" alt="" class="vision-auth-logo vision-auth-logo--light" />
                <p class="vision-auth-wordmark">STUDERRIA</p>
                <h2>Ласкаво просимо</h2>
                <label>
                  <span>Email або імʼя користувача</span>
                  <input type="text" value="" aria-label="Email або імʼя користувача" />
                </label>
                <label>
                  <span>Пароль</span>
                  <input type="password" value="studerria" aria-label="Пароль" />
                </label>
                <button type="button">Увійти</button>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="vision-profile-card" id="profile">
              <header>
                <div class="avatar" aria-hidden="true">MA</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="st-kicker">Profile</p>
                  <h2>Редагування профілю</h2>
                </div>
              </header>
              <div class="vision-profile-stats">
                <span><strong>1</strong>Додано ДЗ</span>
                <span><strong>0</strong>Командні</span>
                <span><strong>0</strong>Бали</span>
              </div>
              <label>
                <span>ПІБ</span>
                <input type="text" value="Марченко Андрій" aria-label="ПІБ" />
              </label>
              <button type="button">Зберегти</button>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="vision-brand-lab" aria-label="Logo and design system usage">
          <article class="vision-brand-card">
            <p class="st-kicker">Logo usage</p>
            <div class="vision-logo-pair">
              <img src="/favicon-dark.png" alt="" />
              <div>
                <strong>Variant 1</strong>
                <span>Навігація, бейджі, favicon, компактні UI-елементи.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vision-logo-pair">
              <img src="/favicon-light.png" alt="" />
              <div>
                <strong>Variant 2</strong>
                <span>Логін, hero, заставки і виразні бренд-поверхні.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="vision-primitive-board">
            <div class="vision-primitive vision-primitive--wide">
              <div>
                <strong>Page background</strong>
                <span>Deep indigo base, restrained ribbons, low-density dust and a hero-scoped ASCII layer.</span>
              </div>
              <span class="st-pill">Dark + Light</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vision-primitive-grid">
              <article class="vision-primitive"><strong>Liquid surface</strong><span>For nav, hero card, auth and elevated focus panels.</span></article>
              <article class="vision-primitive"><strong>Data surface</strong><span>More opaque cards for schedule rows, lists and dense control centers.</span></article>
              <article class="vision-primitive"><strong>Pills + badges</strong><span>One rounded system with restrained tint, border and readable contrast.</span></article>
              <article class="vision-primitive"><strong>Inputs + CTA</strong><span>Quiet outlines, visible focus rings and one premium gradient family.</span></article>
            </div>
          </article>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/vision-bg.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
